		mContext.bindService(service, mDefContainerConn)-->
		mDefContainerConn(连接到服务)-->发送命令sendMessage(OBB_MCS_BOUND, imcs)-->
		-->hanleMessage-->action.execute-->
		
	- 加入action，mActions.add(action)
	}
}

